posting_body: ['Edgewood Park', '1501 145th Place SE, Bellevue\xa0, WA, 98007', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Welcome Home to Edgewood Park', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 845 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Nestled among the evergreens, our garden-style community is ideally located less than ten minutes from major employers such as Microsoft, Boeing and T-Mobile.', 'Offering studio, one, and two bedroom modern apartments for rent in Bellevue, WA, you’ll have no problem finding a home that you’ll love coming home to every day.', 'With the combination of contemporary interiors, relaxing community amenities, and an unbeatable location, what’s not to love about Edgewood Park Apartments?', 'Features', '- Walk-In Closets', '- Energy-Efficient, Stainless-Steel Appliances', '- Designer-Style Kitchen', '- Microwave*', '- Fireplace*', '- 1-12 Month Leasing Options', '- Dishwasher', '- Solid Surface Countertops*', '- Balcony or Patio', '- Plank Floors*', '- Over-Sized Balcony or Patio*', '- Broadband Internet Access', '- Washer/Dryer Hook Ups', '- Garbage Disposal', '- Extra Storage', '- Cable or Satellite', '*In select apartment homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Near Public Transportation', '- On-Site Laundry Facilities', '- Professional Management Team On-Site', '- Recycling Center', '- Community Vegetable Garden', '- Pet Friendly', '- Bike Storage Room', '- Dog Spa', '- Two Sparkling Swimming Pools', '- Fitness Center', '- Clubhouse', '- Emergency Maintenance', '- Package Receiving', '- Online Rental Payments', '- WiFi in Lobby', 'Office Hours', 'Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM', 'Saturday: 10:00 AM to 5:00 PM', 'Sunday: Closed', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats and dogs welcome, fees and restrictions apply.', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'yiyblm2QoSF']
